window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Dawn's life has fallen apart. Instead of going to college, she's broke, unemployed, and single.</p> <p>When her best friend is kidnapped, she starts to wonder if she's actually losing her mind. Was that a demon she saw at the crime scene? And why doesn't anyone remember her friend?</p> <p>Homeless and desperate, Dawn finds herself depending on her mysterious neighbor. Turns out, he belongs to a secretive organization called The Academy of Light - along with four other dangerously sexy men. The Academy seeks to prove monsters are real - and she is now a member.</p> <p>With their protection, Dawn searches for her best friend. But powerful forces want to keep her apart from her guys. If she lets them, she could lose everything - including her life.</p> <p><b>This is a reverse harem urban fantasy series. It is a companion series to Amber Lynn Natusch's </b><b><i>Eve of Eternal Night</i></b><b>.</b></p>"; 
